===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A substance which specifically promotes [[healing]] when [[ingest]]ed or consumed in some way.
# A [[treatment]] or [[cure]].
# The study of the cause, [[diagnosis]], [[prognosis]] and [[treatment]] of [[disease]] or [[illness]].
# The [[profession]] of [[physician]]s, [[surgeon]]s and related specialisms; those who [[practice]] '''medicine'''.
# Ritual [[Native American]] [[magic]] used (notably by a medicine man) to promote a desired outcome in healing, hunting, warfare etc.
# {{obsolete}} [[black magic]], [[superstition]].

